    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# Qualify inbound leads with HubSpot and Slack 24/7\n\n**Pattern:** Lead Capture & Routing · **Level:** Foundation · **Trigger:** Form\n\n## What it does\nQualify inbound leads with HubSpot and Slack 24/7. It starts from a hosted form submission.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual outreach is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nNew Lead Form Submission → Score the Lead → Assign Round-Robin Owner → Route by Heat → Hot → HubSpot + Instant Ping → Notify Assigned Owner → Combine Lead Paths → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to lead capture & routing without manual effort\n- Anyone automating outreach in sales\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Keeps your systems in sync\n- Improves response time\n- Has retries and error handling built in\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: HubSpot private-app token; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.",
        "width": 480,
        "height": 900
      },
